Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:21.23,Normal,Tsukune,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn bạn ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:23.38,Normal,Tsukune,0,0,0,,Mình sẽ trân trọng nó!
