Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.44,Normal,Moka,0,0,0,,Thế nào, Tsukune?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.09,Normal,Moka,0,0,0,,Bạn làm bài tốt chứ?
