Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.68,Normal,Tsukune,0,0,0,,Moka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:16.56,Normal,Moka,0,0,0,,Tsukune!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:20.07,Normal,Tsukune,0,0,0,,Mai vẫn còn bài kiểm tra nữa mà!
